nonUkResident.heading = Are any of the purchasers non-UK resident?
nonUkResident.details.title = What we mean by non-UK resident
nonUkResident.details.d1 = Non-UK resident as an individual
nonUkResident.details.d1.p1 = You are treated as non-UK resident for Stamp Duty Land Tax (SDLT) if you are not present in the UK for 183 days or more in the 12 months before the effective date of the purchase.
nonUkResident.details.d2 = Non-UK resident as a company
nonUkResident.details.d2.p1 = Corporate purchasers will be non-UK resident if they are not UK resident for Corporation Tax purposes on the purchase date.
nonUkResident.details.d2.p2 = Special rules apply for UK resident companies which are under the direct or indirect control of persons who are not resident in the UK.
nonUkResident.details.d2.p3 = Special rules also apply for trusts and settlements.
nonUkResident.error.required = You must complete the effective date field
nonUkResident.error.required = Select ''Yes'' or ''No''

